<HEADLINE>
A MCCAIN MUTINY  
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing. (The Week in Review) 
(js) 
 By ALISON MITCHELL    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ The way Republicans were acting last week it was
almost as if some of them could not decide which was more
uncomfortable: having Pat Buchanan leave the party or John McCain
stay in it.
</P>
<P>
   Unlike Buchanan, McCain, the senior senator from Arizona, has
