<HEADLINE>
GETTING TOUGH GETS TOUGH FOR AUSTRALIA 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(js) 
 By JANE PERLEZ    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
