 &HT;    Captain Underpants is back
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ That goofball hero is back in his third adventure:
``Captain Underpants and the Invasion of the Incredibly Naughty
Cafeteria Ladies From Outer Space (and the Subsequent Assault of
the Equally Evil Lunchroom Zombie Nerds)'' by Dav Pilkey
