   FARM _ Farmland Industries is not through looking for mergers
with other farm cooperatives. By Mark Davis. Graphic
</P>
<P>
   BIXBY _ Kansas City Life chairman Walter Bixby died Monday.
</P>
<P>
   SPORTS BUDGET OFFERS:
</P>
<P>
   THEDOME. A banner hangs lifelessly in the Astrodome these days,
spelling out the fate of perhaps the most famous complex in sports.
``Five more games,'' it resounds across the cavernous dome. The
Astrodome, home of AstroTurf and once a innovation in stadium
design, will hold its last major-league baseball games this week.
Steven Rock. 30.
</P>
<P>
   TIGER. The Royals will become a part of Tiger Stadium history
today when they play in the final home game at the venerable old
ballpark. Photos. Dick Kaegel. 25.
</P>
<P>
   CHIEFS. Folo from the Chiefs' 31-21 victory over Detroit this
