<SLUG> BC-WHEN-PILLS-KILL-ART-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WHEN PILLS KILL  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
   (To purchase this special ``one-shot'' feature from DISCOVER
magazine, contact New York Times Syndicate sales representative
DEBRA WEYDERT at (732) 390-4480; fax, 732-390-4697.)  
 &HT;    
 &HT;    ---------------------FREE ART!----------------------
 &HT;    ONE COLOR ILLUSTRATION showing a heart and pills is available
FREE OF CHARGE to purchasers of this article. The art can be sent
