<SLUG> BC-ODD-BALTIMORE-MAYOR-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MAYOR MARTIN O'MALLEY: BLACK BALTIMORE'S GREAT WHITE HOPE?  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Baltimore, Md.)   (This excellent 800-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 25 Sept. 1999) Economist magazine.)  
  
