<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
POLL (Phoenix) - he latest KAET-TV poll shows the relative
standings in Arizona of the presidential candidates. By CHRIS
MOESER. Story will move in the ``A'' category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
MCTOUR (Phoenix) - This is the official ``kickoff'' tour for John
McCain's presidential campaign. Reporter Jeff Barker is following
along on th e first day. We'll pick him up again in Phoenix on
