<P>
   REAGAN-BOOK (Los Angeles) _ ``Dutch: A Memoir of Ronald
Reagan,'' the long-awaited biography, hits the bookstores Thursday,
but already controversy swirls at the Reagan Library over its
unorthodox nature and some of the facts. The author, Edmund Morris,
