<SLUG> BC-LADN-SPORTS-BUDGET- </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Sept. 27 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Joe Jares at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BBN-STICK (Los Angeles) _ With Candlestick Park (or what used to
Candlestick Park) closing after Thursday's game vs. the Dodgers, we
look at the top 10 Dodgers-Giants moments at the `Stick. 
By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBN-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ On Dodgers shortstop Mark
Grudzielanek. 
By Karen Crouse. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
FBC-UCLA (Los Angeles) _ Cory Paus to start at quarterback again
